===== Install =====
Requirements:
python version 2.6, 2.7
python packages: nosetests(for tests)

The following libraries are downloaded automatically with setup-bosy.sh (Linux):
ltl2ba
z3 solver

Linux
Just run setup.sh to download z3, ltl2ba. If everything went OK then it is ready to use.

OSX
[TODO]

Windows
Under cygwin: run setup.sh, add correct Z3 path to PATH variable or hack bosy.py



===== Test =====
Run 'nosetests .' in the base directory.



===== Run =====
python src/bosy.py
